  <longdescription>
    This ENIGMA package is both the backend and engine to the LateralGM frontend GUI.
    ENIGMA is a developer environment/toolchain used to compile Game Maker games, 
    GML (Game Maker Language) scripts, and EDL (Enigma Development Language)
    scripts that have syntax between GML and C++.
    The ENIGMA engine is the API and the game state mangement offerings and
    management.
  </longdescription>
